title: United Kingdom Imports Intra Eu - Pearls, Precious Stones & Metals & Coins
description: Imports Intra Eu - Pearls, Precious Stones & Metals & Coins in the United Kingdom decreased to 531.28 GBP Million in September from 1087.31 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports Intra Eu - Pearls, Precious Stones & Metal in the United Kingdom averaged 336.83 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 4396.60 GBP Million in March of 2022 and a record low of 37.69 GBP Million in August of 2002.
